{"root":{"data":{"id":"d22q2yzuj480","created":1718671168507,"text":"第四章"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22q3k1dotk0","created":1718671214312,"text":"Micro850 指令系统"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22q59puow80","created":1718671348575,"text":"Micro850 控制器的内存组织"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22q7eon75c0","created":1718671516114,"text":"数据文件"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22q810lem80","created":1718671564726,"text":"Micro850控制器的变量分为全局变量和本地\n变量，其中I/O变量默认为全局变量。全局变量在\n项目的任何一个程序或功能块中都可以使用，而\n本地变量只能在它所在的程序中使用。不同类型\n的控制器I/O变量的类型和个数不同，I/O变量可\n以在CCW组态编程软件中的全局变量中查看。I/O\n变量的名字是固定的，但是可以对I/O变量标记别\n名。除了I/O变量以外，为了编程的需要还要建立\n一些中间变量，变量的类型用户可以自己选择"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22q871b1y80","created":1718671577830,"text":"数据类型 描述"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22q871bcgw0","created":1718671577830,"text":"BOOL 布尔量"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22q871b49s0","created":1718671577830,"text":"SINT 单整型"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22q871ax4o0","created":1718671577830,"text":"USINT、BYTE 无符号单整型"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22q871ausw0","created":1718671577830,"text":"INT、WORD 整型"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22q871awpk0","created":1718671577830,"text":"UINT 无符号整型"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22q871b3l40","created":1718671577830,"text":"DINT、DWORD 双整型"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22q871bm800","created":1718671577831,"text":"UDINT 无符号双整型"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22q871bz3s0","created":1718671577831,"text":"LINT 长整型"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22q871bugw0","created":1718671577831,"text":"ULINT、LWORD 无符号长整型"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22q871bzg00","created":1718671577831,"text":"REAL 实型"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22q871blq80","created":1718671577831,"text":"LREAL 长实型"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22q871bync0","created":1718671577831,"text":"TIME 时间"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22q871bk1c0","created":1718671577831,"text":"DATE 日期"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22q871bvfk0","created":1718671577831,"text":"STRING 字符串"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d22q8i7bmj40","created":1718671602138,"text":"程序文件"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22q8su5zds0","created":1718671625287,"text":"程序（Program）部分"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22q92vcq8o0","created":1718671647127,"text":"功能块（Function Block）部分"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22q9viv4co0","created":1718671709498,"text":"功能块除了系统自身的函数和功能块指令以外，主\n要是指用户根据功能需要，自己编写的具有一定\n功能的功能块，可以在程序（Program）或者功\n能块（Function Block）中调用，相当于常用的子\n程序。"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d22q5pswg680","created":1718671383588,"text":"Micro850控制器的梯形图指令"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22qag83ou80","created":1718671754560,"text":"梯形图指令元素"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22qazpv6vk0","created":1718671796993,"text":"指令块（Instruction blocks）\n块（Block）元素指的是指令块，也可以是位操\n作指令块、函数指令块或者是功能块指令块。在梯\n形图编辑中，可以添加指令块到布尔梯级中。加到\n梯级后可以随时用指令块选择器设置指令块的类型，\n随后相关参数将会自动陈列出来"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d22qalr0cug0","created":1718671766587,"text":"梯形图执行控制指令"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22qb6tiv340","created":1718671812452,"text":" 返回（Returns）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qbdrnxzk0","created":1718671827577,"text":"跳转（Jumps）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qbl7j1y80","created":1718671843774,"text":"分支（Branches）"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d22q6kb2nw00","created":1718671449990,"text":"Micro850控制器的功能块指令"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22qbssck4o0","created":1718671860270,"text":"报警（Alarms） 超过限制值时报警"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qbsscv4o0","created":1718671860270,"text":"布尔运算 （ Boolean operations）对信号上升下降沿以及设置或重置操 作"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qbsscskg0","created":1718671860270,"text":"通讯（Communications） 部件间的通讯操作"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qbsscnug0","created":1718671860270,"text":"计时器（Time） 计时"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qbsscg2o0","created":1718671860270,"text":"计数器（Counter） 计数"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qbsscevc0","created":1718671860270,"text":"数据操作 （ Data manipulation）取平均，最大最小值"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qbssdhsw0","created":1718671860271,"text":"输入/输出（Input/Output） 控制器与模块之间的输入输出操作"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qbsscyao0","created":1718671860271,"text":"中断（Interrupt） 管理中断"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qbssd2ao0","created":1718671860271,"text":"过程控制 （ Process control）PID操作以及堆栈"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qbssczvs0","created":1718671860271,"text":"程序控制 （ Program control）主要是延迟指令功能块"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d22q6tuxrps0","created":1718671470782,"text":"Micro850控制器的功能指令"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22qdvybb200","created":1718672023889,"text":"算术（Arithmetic） 数学算术运算"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qdvybrog0","created":1718672023890,"text":"二进制操作 （ Binary operations）将变量进行二进制运算"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qdvybtgg0","created":1718672023890,"text":"布尔运算（Boolean） 布尔运算"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qdvybnhc0","created":1718672023890,"text":"字符串操作 （ String manipulation）转换提取字符"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qdvyc1540","created":1718672023890,"text":"时间（Time） 确定实时时钟的时间范围，计算时间差"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d22q72fhkao0","created":1718671489439,"text":"用户中断指令"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22qeqvzza80","created":1718672091230,"text":"• STIS可选定时启动"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qeqvzzmo0","created":1718672091230,"text":"• UID 禁止用户中断"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qeqvzzmw0","created":1718672091230,"text":"• UIE允许用户中断"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qeqw06w00","created":1718672091230,"text":"• UIF刷新用户中断"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qeqw05880","created":1718672091230,"text":"• UIC清除用户中断"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d22qevuyju80","created":1718672102051,"text":"Micro850PLC程序设计技术"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22qggqrjhs0","created":1718672225874,"text":"典型环节编程"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22qglvqj740","created":1718672237058,"text":"启保停电路"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qgqlhm0g0","created":1718672247322,"text":"互锁功能"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qgv1751s0","created":1718672256979,"text":"多谐震荡"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d22qh0qxpxc0","created":1718672269420,"text":"PLC控制系统一般设计技术"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22qh9r3fc00","created":1718672289020,"text":"PLC控制系统设计的基本原则"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22qhmd783k0","created":1718672316478,"text":"PLC控制系统控制被控对象应最大限度地满\n足工艺要求。设计前，应深入现场进行调查研究，\n搜索资料，并与机械部分的设计人员和实际操作人\n员密切配合，共同拟定控制方案，协同解决设计中\n出现的各种问题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qhu44u5c0","created":1718672333344,"text":"在满足工艺要求的前提下，力求使PLC控\n制系统简单、经济、使用及维修方便。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qhyio15k0","created":1718672342930,"text":"保证控制系统的安全、可靠"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qi36zilc0","created":1718672353108,"text":"考虑到生产的发展和工艺的改进，在配\n置PLC硬件设备时应适当留有一定的裕量。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d22qhf2jn3s0","created":1718672300596,"text":"PLC控制系统设计的基本内容"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22qibft46o0","created":1718672371055,"text":"选择用户输入设备（按钮、操作开关、\n限位开关、传感器等）、输出设备（继电器、\n接触器、信号灯等执行元件）以及由输出设备\n驱动的控制对象（电动机、电磁阀等）。这些\n设备属于一般的电气元件。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qig9u4ps0","created":1718672381578,"text":"PLC的选择。PLC是PLC控制系统的核心部\n件。正确选择PLC对于保证整个控制系统的技术\n经济性能指标起着重要的作用。选择PLC，包括机型、容量的选择以及I/O模\n块、电源模块等的选择。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22qj26vuxs0","created":1718672429289,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]}]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}